                  <section class="region region-content">
    <article class="node node--type-section-homepage">
  
            <div class="text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"><center>
<h2>Why study at Berklee?</h2>

<p>At Berklee College of Music, you'll deepen your understanding of music, expand your abilities, and collaborate with exceptional artists.Â </p>
</center>

<div class="campus-xref">Note that there is a separate application process for <a class="campus-xref" href="https://online.berklee.edu/degrees/about/undergraduate-degree-admissions-requirements?pid=6580&amp;c3ch=Affiliate&amp;c3nid=bcm_admissions" target="_blank">Berklee Online</a> and <a class="campus-xref" href="https://bostonconservatory.berklee.edu/admissions?pid=036" target="_blank">Boston Conservatory at Berklee</a>.</div></div>
          <div  class="field content-paragraphs">
               
   
<div  class="image-left component horizontal-card" >
  <div class="component-container">
    <div class="content">
    <div class="image-wrapper">
    <img loading="lazy" data-full-src="https://college.berklee.edu/sites/default/files/2020-07/UndergradAdmission_Feature1.jpg?fv=42z79jdW" data-full-width="999" data-full-height="280" src="/sites/default/files/styles/scale_and_crop_8_5_medium/public/2020-07/UndergradAdmission_Feature1.jpg?fv=QyfV5mo-&amp;itok=d3GrqfKg" width="768" height="480" alt="Hands on a controller" class="image-style-scale-and-crop-8-5-medium" />



</div>

    <div class="card-contents">
      <p class="eyebrow">Take the First Step</p>
      <h2>How to Apply</h2>
      <div class="text">
        <p>Get started with these three steps:</p>

<ol><li>Submit the application form.</li>
	<li>Send us your transcript.</li>
	<li>Confirm your audition and/or interview.</li>
</ol>
      </div>
  
      <div class="ctas">
          <a href="/admissions/undergraduate/how-to-apply" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">How to Apply</a>

      </div>
    </div>
