<p>Our <a href="/undergraduate/berklee-boston" title="programs">programs</a> take you beyond the classroom and into the global music scene.</p>

<p>We look for creative and collaborative musicians who possess significantÂ potential and are eager to revolutionize the modern music industry.</p>
